__Description__

The alert is triggered when the Average Count of Dependency Failures over the past 2 days exceeds that of the past 7 days by more than a threshold.

__ Threshold Recommendation__

20 

__ Query __

let avg_failure_7days=dependencies 
| where success  == 'False'
| where timestamp > ago(7d)
|summarize (count()*15)/(7*24*60) ;
let avg_failure_2days=dependencies 
| where success  == 'False'
| where timestamp > ago(2d)
|summarize (count()*15)/(2*24*60) ;
dependencies
| where timestamp > ago(2d)
| where success  == 'False'
| extend avg_Failure_7days=toscalar(avg_failure_7days)
| extend avg_Failure_2days=toscalar(avg_failure_2days)
| extend Difference = avg_Failure_2days - avg_Failure_7days
| summarize AggregatedValue=avg(Difference) by bin (timestamp,2d)
settings.title: Alert for High increase in dependency Failure

settings.content:
__ Description __

Alert can be triggered when the Percentage Increase of a bin (5min each) within 5 days is more than the rolling average of exception count for  past 10 days period beyond a threshold.

__ Threshold__

150
Consecutively for 5 bins (5 min each)


__ Query __

let avg_exception_10d = exceptions | where timestamp > ago(10d)
| summarize Count_5min = (count()/(10*24*60))*5;
exceptions
| where timestamp > ago(5d)
| summarize Count=count() by bin(timestamp,5m)
| extend percent_change = toint(((Count- toscalar(avg_exception_10d))*100/toscalar(avg_exception_10d)))
// | where percent_increase > 0
|summarize avg(percent_change) by bin(timestamp,5m)
// | where percent_increase >threshold
| render columnchart with (title="Exception Percentage Change (over 5/10 days)")
settings.title: Alert for High Percentage Increase in Exceptions

Triggers an alert when Availaible Memory falls below a Threshold

1 GB
1 consecutive bin (30 min)

settings.content:
__ Description __

Alert can be triggered when the Percentage Increase of a bin (15 min each) within 6 hrs is more than the rolling average of exception count for  past 2 days period beyond a threshold.

__ Threshold__

240
Consecutively for 4 bins (15 min each)

__ Signal Logic __

let avg_exception_2d = exceptions| where timestamp > ago(2d)  
| summarize Count_15min = (count()*15/(2*24*60));  
exceptions  
| union app('appinsights-car-api-prod-usc').exceptions  
| where timestamp > ago(6h)  
| summarize Count=count() by bin(timestamp,15m)  
| extend percent_change = toint(((Count- toscalar(avg_exception_2d))*100/toscalar(avg_exception_2d)))  
| summarize AggregatedValue= avg(percent_change) by bin(timestamp,15m)
settings.title: Alert for High Percentage Increase in Exceptions

__Description__

The alert is triggered when the Average Count of Dependency Failures over the last 6 hours exceeds that of the past 2 days by more than a threshold.

let avg_failure_2days=dependencies  
| where success  == 'False' 
| where timestamp > ago(2d) 
|summarize (count()*15)/(2*24*60); 
let avg_failure_6h=dependencies

| where timestamp > ago(6h) 
|summarize (count()*15/(60*6)); 
dependencies

| where success  == 'False' 
| extend avg_failure_2days=toscalar(avg_failure_2days) 
| extend avg_failure_6h=toscalar(avg_failure_6h) 
| extend Difference = avg_failure_6h - avg_failure_2days 
| summarize AggregatedValue=avg(Difference) by bin (timestamp,15m)
